  "content": [
    {
      "chapterUid": 19,
      "chapterTitle": "第8章 什么是量子算法",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300105089_19_540-586",
          "range": "540-586",
          "rangeStart": 540,
          "rangeEnd": 586,
          "markText": "量子算法的一个重要应用是提升解决问题的速度，在这些问题中，需要搜索我们试图了解的函数的输入。",
          "colorStyle": 0,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1751617525,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2025-07-04 16:25:25",
          "chapterUid": 19,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300105089&chapterUid=19&rangeStart=540&rangeEnd=586",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/fda32cf0813ab8f8cg0198e6?chapterUid=19&rangeStart=540&rangeEnd=586"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "chapterUid": 22,
      "chapterTitle": "第10章 用量子计算机解决化学问题",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300105089_22_48236-48282",
          "range": "48236-48282",
          "rangeStart": 48236,
          "rangeEnd": 48282,
          "markText": "较复杂的哈密顿算符可以分解为较简单的哈密顿算符之和，这使我们可以同时模拟哈密顿算符的每一项。",
          "colorStyle": 0,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1751617516,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2025-07-04 16:25:16",
          "chapterUid": 22,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300105089&chapterUid=22&rangeStart=48236&rangeEnd=48282",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/fda32cf0813ab8f8cg0198e6?chapterUid=22&rangeStart=48236&rangeEnd=48282"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "bookReviews": [],
  "hotBookmarks": [
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300105089_28_1493-1573",
      "chapterUid": 28,
      "range": "1493-1573",
      "markText": "从历史上看，.NET是.NET Framework的合理简称，是任何一种.NET语言（如C#、F#和Visual Basic.NET）的虚拟机和编译器基础结构。",
      "totalCount": 77,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300105089&chapterUid=28&rangeStart=1493&rangeEnd=1573",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/fda32cf0813ab8f8cg0198e6?chapterUid=28&rangeStart=1493&rangeEnd=1573"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300105089_28_2812-2870",
      "chapterUid": 28,
      "range": "2812-2870",
      "markText": "有一件事可能与你的习惯不同，那就是.NET开发的中心思想是“项目”，它指定了如何调用编译器来制作一个新的二进制文件。",
      "totalCount": 77,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300105089&chapterUid=28&rangeStart=2812&rangeEnd=2870",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/fda32cf0813ab8f8cg0198e6?chapterUid=28&rangeStart=2812&rangeEnd=2870"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300105089_11_2146-2173",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "2146-2173",
      "markText": "同时，量子计算机并不是灵丹妙药——有些问题仍然会很难。",
      "totalCount": 75,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300105089&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=2146&rangeEnd=2173",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/fda32cf0813ab8f8cg0198e6?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=2146&rangeEnd=2173"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300105089_13_23881-23938",
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "23881-23938",
      "markText": "作为对“不可克隆定理”的另一种思考方式，Bob如果能够在不干扰量子位的情况下测量它，就无须他所截获的量子位的副本。",
      "totalCount": 71,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300105089&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=23881&rangeEnd=23938",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/fda32cf0813ab8f8cg0198e6?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=23881&rangeEnd=23938"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300105089_18_4563-4611",
      "chapterUid": 18,
      "range": "4563-4611",
      "markText": "Q#程序被发送到模拟器上，但在这种情况下，模拟器只是运行经典逻辑，因为还没有需要考虑的量子指令。",
      "totalCount": 71,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300105089&chapterUid=18&rangeStart=4563&rangeEnd=4611",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/fda32cf0813ab8f8cg0198e6?chapterUid=18&rangeStart=4563&rangeEnd=4611"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300105089_18_22963-23026",
      "chapterUid": 18,
      "range": "22963-23026",
      "markText": "例如，在清单7.8中，我们使用了一个MResetZ操作，它既可以测量一个量子位（类似于M），又可以重置它（类似于Reset）。",
      "totalCount": 71,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300105089&chapterUid=18&rangeStart=22963&rangeEnd=23026",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/fda32cf0813ab8f8cg0198e6?chapterUid=18&rangeStart=22963&rangeEnd=23026"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300105089_11_962-1015",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "962-1015",
      "markText": "前进的道路就是批判性地理解量子计算提供的承诺、量子计算机的工作原理、量子计算的范围是什么（以及不是什么）。",
      "totalCount": 70,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300105089&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=962&rangeEnd=1015",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/fda32cf0813ab8f8cg0198e6?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=962&rangeEnd=1015"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300105089_11_2069-2146",
